edu.ucsd.ccdb.ontomorph2.core.scene
Interface INeuronMorphology

All Superinterfaces:
ISceneObject, ISelectable
All Known Implementing Classes:
NeuronMorphologyImpl
public interface INeuronMorphology
extends ISceneObject

Describes the morphology of the cell, independent of different ways of visualizing it. Since it is a three-dimensional morphology, this will describe points in a local 3D space (MorphML?)

Author:
Stephen D. Larson (slarson@ncmir.ucsd.edu)
